sentences.sentence: If for any reason it appears to the Registrar that a ship in respect of which an application for registration has been made may not be registrable.
sentences.translation: 注册官如因任何理由认为申请人申请予以注册的船舶不可注册。

sentences.sentence: Chapter 2 "Definition of 'Prior Trademark'" discusses such issues as the unregistered and registrable status of the prior trademark and the related time limit;
